scenes.description: Announcement text for Moona Hoshinova's 1st album 'PANDORA' pre-orders.
Moona Hoshinova introduces the tracks and editions of her first album 'PANDORA'.
Ending message from Moona to her fans, displayed as on-screen text with instrumental music.

subtitles.original:
MOONA HOSHINOVA "PANDORA"
Pre-orders open today at 22:00 JST / 20:00 WIB!
subtitles.english:
MOONA HOSHINOVA "PANDORA"
Pre-orders open today at 22:00 JST / 20:00 WIB!

subtitles.original: This will be the first album from hololive Indonesia.
subtitles.english: This will be the first album from hololive Indonesia.

subtitles.original: The album includes four brand new songs,
subtitles.english: The album includes four brand new songs,

subtitles.original: including the collaboration track 100% with Nerissa, which I just performed today.
subtitles.english: including the collaboration track 100% with Nerissa, which I just performed today.

subtitles.original: It also features previously released songs
subtitles.english: It also features previously released songs

subtitles.original: like Nightmare from last year, making a total of 10 tracks.
subtitles.english: like Nightmare from last year, making a total of 10 tracks.

subtitles.original: The CD comes in two editions:
subtitles.english: The CD comes in two editions:

subtitles.original: Limited Bonus Edition and Regular Edition.
subtitles.english: Limited Bonus Edition and Regular Edition.

subtitles.original: Limited Bonus Edition includes a CD jacket with my handwritten autograph.
subtitles.english: Limited Bonus Edition includes a CD jacket with my handwritten autograph.

subtitles.original: This is a one-of-a-kind autograph just for you.
subtitles.english: This is a one-of-a-kind autograph just for you.

subtitles.original: Comes with an online meet & greet lottery application ticket,
subtitles.english: Comes with an online meet & greet lottery application ticket,

subtitles.original: plus a special letter from Moona and two clear bookmarks.
subtitles.english: plus a special letter from Moona and two clear bookmarks.

subtitles.original: It's a super deluxe package!
subtitles.english: It's a super deluxe package!

subtitles.original: Regular Edition comes with one random trading card.
subtitles.english: Regular Edition comes with one random trading card.

subtitles.original: There are four different types plus one secret type.
subtitles.english: There are four different types plus one secret type.

subtitles.original: Can't wait to see which one you get!
subtitles.english: Can't wait to see which one you get!

subtitles.original: Pre-orders open right after this
subtitles.english: Pre-orders open right after this

subtitles.original: on the hololive production OFFICIAL SHOP. Make sure to grab your copy!
subtitles.english: on the hololive production OFFICIAL SHOP. Make sure to grab your copy!

subtitles.original: By the way, the digital album is set to release on April 12th,
subtitles.english: By the way, the digital album is set to release on April 12th,

subtitles.original: the day after my first ever livestream anniversary.
subtitles.english: the day after my first ever livestream anniversary.

subtitles.original: Thank you for all your incredible support.
subtitles.english: Thank you for all your incredible support.

subtitles.original: I wouldn't be able to make music without you.
subtitles.english: I wouldn't be able to make music without you.

subtitles.original: Moona Hoshinova, PANDORA.
subtitles.english: Moona Hoshinova, PANDORA.

subtitles.original: Hope you're as excited as I am!
subtitles.english: Hope you're as excited as I am!

subtitles.original: Thank you for coming to my 3D Birthday ✨
subtitles.english: Thank you for coming to my 3D Birthday ✨

subtitles.original: your love and support make everything shine even brighter!
subtitles.english: your love and support make everything shine even brighter!

subtitles.original: It's been an incredible-almost 5 years together and
subtitles.english: It's been an incredible-almost 5 years together and

subtitles.original: I can't wait to make even more amazing memories with all of you! ♡
subtitles.english: I can't wait to make even more amazing memories with all of you! ♡

subtitles.original: Let's keep shining together !!!
